      <title>以色列在战争“新阶段”扩大对真主党的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/israel-widens-strikes-against-hezbollah-in-new-phase-of-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列周四对黎巴嫩南部地区实施了大规模空袭，在宣布对该地区激进组织真主党的战争进入“新阶段”后，敌对行动进一步升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/israel-widens-strikes-against-hezbollah-in-new-phase-of-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 07:27:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国 8 月零售销售好于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/uk-retail-sales-beat-expectations-during-sunny-spell-in-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者渴望享受晴朗天气和夏季折扣，抵消了日益加剧的政治和财政忧虑，英国八月份零售额加速增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/uk-retail-sales-beat-expectations-during-sunny-spell-in-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 06:10:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾参议员称以中国为中心的赌场与集团有关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/philippine-china-centric-casinos-seen-deeply-tied-to-syndicates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责该行业调查的一位议员周五表示，罗德里戈·杜特尔特总统任期内在菲律宾蓬勃发展的以中国为中心的在线赌场可能与国际犯罪集团有“深厚联系”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/philippine-china-centric-casinos-seen-deeply-tied-to-syndicates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 05:19:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国被领养儿童指控西方国家对“邮购儿童”视而不见</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-20/western-nations-were-desperate-for-korean-babies-now-many-adoptees-believe-they-were-stolen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金尤莉走进巴黎的一家警察局，告诉警官她想报案。她说，40 年前，她在世界的另一端被绑架，法国政府批准了她的报案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-20/western-nations-were-desperate-for-korean-babies-now-many-adoptees-believe-they-were-stolen</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 04:32:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国表示愿意恢复从日本进口海鲜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/japan-eyes-deal-to-end-chinese-ban-on-seafood-imports-media-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国与东京就福岛核电站废水排放问题达成协议后，表示愿意恢复进口日本海产品。]]></description>
