    <item>
      <title>台湾法院裁定限制适用死刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/top-taiwan-court-to-rule-on-legal-challenge-to-death-penalty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾大法官法庭维持死刑的合法性，但限制死刑的使用，这一决定在保持死刑的威慑力与防止死刑滥用之间取得了平衡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/top-taiwan-court-to-rule-on-legal-challenge-to-death-penalty</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>核能复兴让日本首相候选人团结起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/nuclear-power-revival-unites-japan-s-prime-minister-contenders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本可能仍在努力应对福岛核灾难的深远影响，但争夺下一任领导人的政客们一致同意一件事：这个国家需要更多的核能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/nuclear-power-revival-unites-japan-s-prime-minister-contenders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰铢升值 1998 年以来最大 泰国旅游业和出口面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/baht-s-biggest-rally-since-1998-threatens-thai-tourism-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国泰铢即将创下亚洲金融危机以来的最大季度涨幅，这可能会影响该国主要旅游业和出口业的复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/baht-s-biggest-rally-since-1998-threatens-thai-tourism-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>传呼机爆炸敲响全球供应链安全警钟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/exploding-pagers-sound-global-alarm-for-supply-chain-security</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，黎巴嫩发生数千台传呼机和其他设备爆炸，标志着利用供应链对敌人发起攻击的行动再次升级，造成致命后果。这也使全球领导人更加迫切地需要减少对竞争对手技术的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/exploding-pagers-sound-global-alarm-for-supply-chain-security</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 20:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
