      <title>马斯克的特斯拉工厂成为德国州投票争议的焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/tesla-could-help-far-right-secure-win-in-german-state-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉在欧洲的第一家工厂原本有望为柏林附近地区带来数千个就业岗位和数百万美元的额外税收收入，从而振兴该地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/tesla-could-help-far-right-secure-win-in-german-state-vote</guid>
